{"tid":1094244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果音樂美付費用戶量已超Spotify","createTime":"2019-04-06T06:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T07:40:56.000Z","uid":30081,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7125cd0cf37d6f85c32d213410e8b4cd98487d1b","tid":1094244,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"蘋果音樂的美國付費用戶數量，已經超越了Spotify，可見主流媒體的音樂服務競爭出現轉折，這也提前預示了蘋果公司新服務戰略將取得成功，該戰略旨在向現有iPhone用戶銷售月度在線服務。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述知情人士指出，蘋果音樂2月在美國有2800萬付費用戶，而Spotify有2600萬付費用戶，同時蘋果音樂在全球和美國的增長率亦高於Spotify，但Spotify的訂閱用戶總數仍然高於蘋果音樂。<br />\n<br />\nSpotify和Apple關係不佳，上月Spotify首席執行官斥責蘋果在其應用商店實行不公平政策，並向歐盟委員會提出反壟斷投訴。蘋果公司在其網站上的一份聲明中回應，Spotify正在用誤導性言辭掩蓋其財務動機。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果和Spotify均拒絕置評。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2104239/蘋果音樂美付費用戶量已超Spotify\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2104239%2F%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E7%BE%8E%E4%BB%98%E8%B2%BB%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E9%87%8F%E5%B7%B2%E8%B6%85Spotify&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=4d0e67e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2104239/蘋果音樂美付費用戶量已超Spotify</a>"},{"pid":"8102c906ce6b6c4458b673f17a5ec8e61c550180","tid":1094244,"uid":72009,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"apple 往往不是先入某產品市場，但卻打敗市場number one"},{"pid":"332928d008c3b26e4c6103da520dfe391b90aae0","tid":1094244,"uid":68094,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49a704619171804c6e36d2b42363fa38400a7950","tid":1094244,"uid":196459,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"apple music好垃圾喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6b0b8e5f5d86947e29e5a8a183ddb7543f88e1","tid":1094244,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike